This map has now 4 levels and 1 choosing level (Race):

    Easy: GO TO THE PATH YOU WANT:
        This is the only mod with HELICOPTER IN THE BEGINNING!!!!!!;
        You have only 1 hold spot (the door);
        After the door close (you need to wait 90 seconds to the door opens), a nuke will appear and the Easy level is completed.

    Normal: GO ONLY UPON THE ROOFS:
        YOU DONT HAVE HELICOPTER IN THIS MOD;
        You ONLY can go UPON THE ROOFS;
        You have only 2 hold spots (in the tallest building, 20 seconds to cover, and the door, 90 seconds to cover);
        After the door closes, a nuke will appear and the Normal level is completed.

    Hard: GO ONLY UNDER THE ROOFS:
        YOU DONT HAVE HELICOPTER IN THIS MOD;
        You need to go UNDER THE ROOFS;
        You have 3 hold spots (25 seconds under the roofs, 15 seconds near the crusher and 90 seconds in the door);
        After door opens and go into the building, ~6 seconds later a dodge will appear (ITS 4 DODDGES , 1 PER ROUND AND RANDOM);
        After the dodge, the door will close in 5 seconds, the nuke will appear and the Hard level is COMPLETED;
        In this level, humans have 125HP and zombies have 50000HP;

    -Extreme: GO ONLY BEHIND THE BASES:
        YOU ONLY HAVE HELICOPTER IN THE END OF THE MAP;
        Zombies has 50000HP and humans have 125HP;
        You have 5 hold spots (Near crusher, in the tallest building, 2 in the center of the map and the helicopter waiting spot);
        The helicopter will appear after 75 seconds and leave 15 seconds before reaching the spot area);
        After the helicopter stops, the EXTREME LEVEL IS COMPLETED AND NEXT IS RACE;

    Race Mod: YOU HAVE 45 SECONDS TO CHOOSE THE LEVEL:
        YOU DONT HAVE HELICOPTER IN THIS MOD;
        You only have 45 seconds to choose the level;
        After the 45 seconds, the nuke will appear and will kill all players.

